column2:
"Wow, you can really feel the ambient
magic here. I was getting a sense
of it from outside the forest, but
inside is like nothing I've ever seen."

"I'm picking up Ephimera readings, but
this forest must have already been
pretty weird. And look over there."

"There aren't any human life
signs around here, but there's
lots of Demons and Darkers.
Who could be summoning them...?"

"Anything could happen here. Please
be very careful as you proceed."
